<% layout("/layouts/dashboard") %>
<br><br>
<div class="container my-5 " style="max-width:900px;">

    <h2 class="mb-4 ">Safety & Security</h2>

    <p>
        At <strong>StayVerse</strong>, your safety is our top priority. We are committed to providing a secure and trustworthy platform for both guests and hosts across India.
    </p>

    <hr>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🏡 For Guests</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Always review property details, images, and ratings before booking.</li>
        <li>Communicate with hosts only through the StayVerse platform.</li>
        <li>Do not share personal or payment information outside the platform.</li>
        <li>Check location details and nearby landmarks before arrival.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🏠 For Hosts</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Verify guest details before accepting bookings.</li>
        <li>Keep your listing information accurate and updated.</li>
        <li>Ensure your property meets safety and hygiene standards.</li>
        <li>Provide emergency contact details for guests.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🚨 Emergency Support</h4>
    <p>
        In case of any emergency, please contact local authorities immediately:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Police:</strong> 100</li>
        <li><strong>Ambulance:</strong> 102</li>
        <li><strong>Fire:</strong> 101</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🔐 Platform Safety Measures</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Secure payment processing</li>
        <li>Verified user accounts</li>
        <li>Review and rating system</li>
        <li>Report and support system for issues</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">📩 Report a Safety Issue</h4>
    <p>
        If you encounter any unsafe behavior or suspicious activity, please report it immediately through our 
        <a href="/report-issue">Report Issue</a> page.
    </p>

    <hr>

    <p class="text-muted">
        Stay safe and enjoy your journey with StayVerse ❤️
    </p>

</div>